message:
Running command: cd /workspace/SheepVibes && git add . && git commit -m "fix: address PR #95 review comments

- CORS allowed origins now configurable via CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS environment variable

message.content:
Perfect! Now I have successfully addressed both review comments from PR #95:

1. ✅ **MEDIUM PRIORITY**: CORS allowed origins are now configurable via environment variables
2. ✅ **HIGH PRIORITY**: Cache invalidation now happens immediately after feed properties are updated, regardless of whether new items are found

Let me commit and push these fixes:
